    "body": "@\nParent: #244. **BLOCKED by the Track A validation gate \u2014 do not start until 3/5 QA yeses.**\n\nRe-integrate the Track B perf pair from `track-b-c-deferred/cherenkov/execution/`:\n- `k6_runner.py` (`K6Runner`) \u2014 exports a k6 JS script and runs it to capture metrics.\n- `perf_analyzer.py` (`PerformanceAnalyzer`) \u2014 records round-trip latency in SQLite and flags regressions.\n\n**Acceptance (post-gate):**\n- Graceful degrade when the `k6` binary is absent (detect + honest message, no silent skip).\n- SQLite store under `.cherenkov/`; avoid colliding with `rag_store.db` (the deferred copy reuses that path \u2014 give perf its own DB).\n- Measured metrics only \u2014 no simulated values (cf. #157 \"perf metrics simulated, not measured\").\n- Unit test for the regression-flagging math.\n\nReframes closed #12.\n@",
