    "body": "@\nParent: #244. **BLOCKED by the Track A validation gate \u2014 do not start until 3/5 QA yeses.**\n\nRe-integrate `track-b-c-deferred/cherenkov/execution/visual_diff.py` (`VisualDiffEngine`) \u2014 Playwright `toHaveScreenshot` baseline capture + structural diffing \u2014 into the supported `cherenkov/` surface.\n\n**Acceptance (post-gate):**\n- Move into `cherenkov/execution/` with unit + smoke coverage.\n- Baselines stored under `.cherenkov/`, not `stub/generated_tests/` (the deferred copy writes into stub paths \u2014 fix the suggest-only boundary, cf. #219).\n- Honest provenance: no fabricated pass; surfaces \"no baseline \u2192 initialized\" explicitly.\n- Wire to a real Signals/visual screen in `cherenkov/web/ui/` only if data is live (else MOCK badge per #239).\n\nReframes closed #11 as re-integration.\n@",
